{"tid":912126,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日擬成立「宇宙部隊」監控衞星","createTime":"2018-11-22T12:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T13:32:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fa51fa2c748bb2d33aba26ce8d5c0b07d40c96c6","tid":912126,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T12:15:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181122/20551724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F20551724&d=gBevDKq4SDLeIAghxjmgyZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=ce3edd83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F20551724&h=6bbac116\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181122/20551724</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月22日 <br />\n<br />\n日擬成立「宇宙部隊」監控衞星<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181122/large/22wh61p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181122%2Flarge%2F22wh61p.jpg&h=41b3c9aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安倍晉三政府希望來年國防加強太空監控。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本政府正草擬新一份《防衞計劃大綱》，計劃集中投放資源提升太空監控及網絡保安，包括成立「宇宙部隊」，來監視太空垃圾和別國可疑衞星的動態。按計劃，這支部隊會在2022年完成組建。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n料2022年成立<br />\n<br />\n繼美國特朗普政府打算在2020年前爭取國會支持成立美國「太空軍」後，日本政府前日也在安全保障及防衞力量座談會闡述新一份防衞大綱草案時，提出了成立「宇宙部隊」，料2022年完成組建。<br />\n<br />\n由於現時太空上有不少過期或損壞的人造衞星及火箭，這些太空垃圾會威脅到其他衞星或火箭的運作。因此，防衞省擬成立「宇宙部隊」，通過地面和飛行器上的雷達，時刻監測太空垃圾的情況。另外，部隊亦能監察別國衞星的舉動，提防任何太空威脅。<br />\n<br />\n草案亦有在使用尖端防衞技術上着墨，包括提議引進激光技術及人工智能（AI），如研發大型無人駕駛潛艇等。另外，隨着人口減少及老化帶來的人手短缺問題日趨嚴重，當局提出以善用科技節省人力，又要以取錄更多自衞官、提高待遇和延長退休年齡等措施，吸引並挽留人才。<br />\n<br />\n中新社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n韓方解散慰安婦和解基金會"},{"pid":"16c8520c1dcd27cdd125fc59050cccbbfdf1a9f6","tid":912126,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:22:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=HYMEts2ASEY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHYMEts2ASEY&d=gBevDKq4SDLeIAghxjmgyZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=377ad778\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=HYMEts2ASEY</a>"},{"pid":"40cce1690a652b6b44b1eb0f3aa459e3169a9eba","tid":912126,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"準備好打外星人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed30daf31fe5d2ccc7230d3f3b59ffc27bf0ee89","tid":912126,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:32:51.000Z","msg":"渣古出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}